<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\">When you sign up for an account at MailChimp, you're constantly monitored for any signs of abuse. When MailChimp sees things that need explaining on your end, or investigating on their end, your account may be flagged and the review team might take some time to check things out. For a list of Red Flags view this MailChimp article:&nbsp;http:\/\/kb.mailchimp.com\/article\/why-was-my-account-suspended\/&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Here are the things you can do to speed up the review process by MailChimp:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ol style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li>Make sure your account is compliant with MailChimp's&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #158ec2; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\" title=\"terms of use\" href=\"http:\/\/mailchimp.com\/legal\/terms\/\">Terms of Use<\/a>.<\/li>\r\n<li>Set up a list and a campaign that includes real content that you actually plan on sending to your list.&nbsp;<strong>MailChimp&nbsp;can&rsquo;t begin the review process until a campaign and list are in place.<\/strong><\/li>\r\n<li>Check to see that you have a good Permission Reminder in place for all lists in your account. You'll find the Permission Reminder under&nbsp;<em>Lists &gt; settings &gt; required email footer content<\/em>. Need some help? Here are some pointers on&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #158ec2; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\" title=\"how to write a good permission reminder\" href=\"http:\/\/www.mailchimp.com\/blog\/what-makes-a-good-permission-reminder\/\">What Makes a Good Permission Reminder<\/a>.<\/li>\r\n<li>Include a valid postal address in any campaigns you plan on sending through us. A postal address is&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #158ec2; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\" title=\"can-spam requirements\" href=\"http:\/\/kb.mailchimp.com\/article\/what-is-required-to-meet-your-terms-of-use-and-the-can-spam-act\">required by the Federal Can-Spam Act<\/a>, so MailChimp has to make sure you include it.<\/li>\r\n<\/ol>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #158ec2; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\" href=\"\/hc\/en-us\/articles\/201907598-Why-is-my-MailChimp-account-suspended-\" target=\"_blank\">Why is my MailChimp account suspended?<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">Login to&nbsp;<\/span><a style=\"color: #1155cc; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http:\/\/datavalidation.com\/login\" target=\"_blank\">My Account<\/a><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;| Go&nbsp;to&nbsp;<\/span><a style=\"color: #1155cc; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http:\/\/datavalidation.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">DataValidation.com<\/a><\/p>",
